<section id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Since 2009, Garden Home Health Care, Inc. has been a trusted provider of home-based care services across the Twin Cities, seven metro counties, and southern Minnesota. As a family-owned agency, we approach every client with genuine care, respect, and attention to detail.</p>
